      <div class="pipeline">

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node current"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="tag tag-current">current</span>
              <span class="mono dim">Feb 2025 — Present</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Remote DevOps Engineer</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">CoverMore Group (UK) <span class="dim">— via Tech Bridge Consultancy, outsourced</span></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Outsourced by Tech Bridge Consultancy to CoverMore Group's UK office as a remote DevOps engineer.</li>
              <li>Manage and maintain Data Warehouse infrastructure on AWS with full infrastructure-as-code using Terraform.</li>
              <li>Build and maintain ETL pipelines and data workflows using AWS Glue, Step Functions, Lambda, S3, and Redshift.</li>
              <li>Automate deployments and releases through Bitbucket CI/CD pipelines.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node current"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="tag tag-current">current</span>
              <span class="mono dim">Mar 2025 — Present</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Part-Time AWS DevOps Engineer</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">Ageasis Lab</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Deployed a serverless Android application backend using AWS SAM and CloudFormation.</li>
              <li>Managed a 14-Lambda microservices architecture integrated with API Gateway, RDS, VPC, and Amazon Cognito for authentication and data management.</li>
              <li>Configured secure, scalable infrastructure ensuring seamless integration across all AWS services.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="mono dim">Jun 2025 — Jan 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>DevOps Engineer</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">Tech Bridge Consultancy <span class="dim">— Lahore</span></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Provided technical support and administration for internal networks, pfSense firewall, and infrastructure monitoring systems.</li>
              <li>Managed day-to-day DevOps and infrastructure operations with development and internal IT teams.</li>
              <li>Administered Proxmox virtualization environments and multiple AWS accounts.</li>
              <li>Monitored and optimized cloud usage across AWS and DigitalOcean, with a focus on billing analysis and cost optimization.</li>
              <li>Deployed, maintained, and troubleshot cloud infrastructure for high availability and performance.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="mono dim">Oct 2023 — Feb 2025</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Associate DevOps Engineer</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">Sudo Consultants <span class="dim">— Karachi</span></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Managed and supported cloud infrastructure for high-transaction POS-based client systems.</li>
              <li>Provided L2 support for AWS services: EC2, ECS, RDS, ALB/ELB, Route53.</li>
              <li>Automated infrastructure using Terraform, Ansible, Jenkins, and GitLab CI/CD.</li>
              <li>Deployed and maintained containerized applications using Docker and AWS ECS.</li>
              <li>Implemented monitoring and alerting with Prometheus, Grafana, and CloudWatch.</li>
              <li>Managed SSL/TLS, Let's Encrypt, Certbot, and mTLS, integrated with Route53 and Cloudflare.</li>
              <li>Performed AWS environment migrations from staging to production and configured VPCs, security groups, and VPC peering.</li>
              <li>Supported Azure integrations including VPN setup and enterprise applications.</li>
              <li>Executed infrastructure migrations from shared hosting to AWS EC2 with minimal downtime.</li>
              <li>Provided 24/7 production support and resolved critical infrastructure issues.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="mono dim">Oct 2019 — Aug 2020</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Customer Service Representative</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">Pakistan Telecom Company Limited <span class="dim">— Karachi</span></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Handled customer data, logged issue histories, and ensured proper documentation in CRM systems.</li>
              <li>Consistently resolved technical issues, providing timely feedback and clear summaries to supervisors.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="deploy">
          <div class="deploy-rail"><span class="deploy-node end"></span></div>
          <div class="deploy-body">
            <div class="deploy-meta">
              <span class="mono dim">Feb 2018 — Feb 2019</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Network Engineer</h3>
            <div class="deploy-org">Express News Network <span class="dim">— Karachi</span></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Managed critical broadcast systems and documented network changes, policies, and escalations.</li>
              <li>Supported IT with written summaries for troubleshooting and compliance checks.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>

