          <h3>Data Warehouse Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>Designed and deployed a scalable data warehouse solution on AWS with fully automated ETL and migration workflows.</p>
          <ul class="project-list">
            <li>ETL &amp; migration workflows via Glue Jobs, DMS, Step Functions, Lambda, and Redshift.</li>
            <li>Integrated S3, SNS, Secrets Manager, and KMS for storage, notifications, and encryption.</li>
            <li>Fully automated provisioning with Terraform and Bitbucket CI/CD.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">Terraform</span><span class="tag">Glue</span><span class="tag">Redshift</span><span class="tag">Lambda</span>
