          <h3>Serverless Android Application Deployment</h3>
          <p>Deployed a serverless backend for an Android application using AWS SAM and CloudFormation.</p>
          <ul class="project-list">
            <li>Managed 14 Lambda functions integrated with API Gateway, RDS, VPC, and Amazon Cognito.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">AWS SAM</span><span class="tag">CloudFormation</span><span class="tag">Cognito</span>
